'''桑塞尔'''（{{lang-fr|Sancerre}}，{{IPA-fr|sɑ̃sɛʁ|-|Fr-Paris--Sancerre.ogg}}）是位于[[法国|法国]][[卢瓦尔河|卢瓦尔河]]西岸[[桑塞尔_(谢尔省)|桑塞尔]]地区的[[葡萄酒|葡萄酒]][[原产地命名控制|法定产区]]，比邻卢瓦尔河东岸的[[普伊芙美|普伊芙美]]产区。

桑塞尔产区于1936年起成为法定产区，主要以由[[白苏维翁|长相思]]葡葡酿成的[[干白葡萄酒|干白葡萄酒]]而闻名。<ref>E. Asimov ''"[http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/15/dining/reviews/15wine.html Sancerre: Say It With Feeling] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/15/dining/reviews/15wine.html |date=20160620035443 }}"'' New York Times, April 15th, 2009</ref>此外，该产区也种植[[黑比诺|黑比诺]]葡萄（占约五分之一）<ref>J. Ray ''[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/foodanddrink/wine/4323508/Top-10-Loire-wines.html Top 10 Loire wines] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/foodanddrink/wine/4323508/Top-10-Loire-wines.html |date=20170125075411 }}"'' The Telegraph, January 28th, 2009</ref>，并出产由此酿成的[[干红葡萄酒|干红葡萄酒]]与[[桃红葡萄酒|桃红葡萄酒]]。<ref name="Bespaloff pg 90-94">A. Bespaloff ''Complete Guide to Wine'' pg 90-94 Penguin Books 1994 ISBN 0-451-18169-7</ref><ref name="Rob pg 180-182">J. Robinson ''Jancis Robinson's Wine Course'' Third Edition pg 180-182 Abbeville Press 2003 ISBN 0-7892-0883-0</ref>

